((I'm at my friends house posting))

Tigerhawk keeps a steady stride walking in circle "I thought the reason for 
this journey was to get stronger all we've found is one stone tablet that 
hand this picture and you set under that waterfall for 3 days doing nothing. 
Well, say something are you even alive over there."


Liono sits on a rock under as waterfall crashes down on him Liono's eye are 
black almost as if he is offline.

Tigerhawk Reaches in the water fall to touch Liono as the water hits his hand 
he draws back "its freezing my servos it" 

Liono stands up in the waterfalls his eye turn blue and as cold as ice as 
blue beam shoots out of his optics freezing the waterfall.

Tigerhawk stops "how did you do that you never had ice beams?" 
 
Liono steps away from the waterfall "look at the seal on the rock I was 
sitting on"

Tigerhawk looks the seal "seal of the vok but that would mean you took what 
ever was in the seal into yourself and it was the Ice beam" 

Liono "right" watches as the seal disappear.  Holds up the tablet next looks 
like next we head west towards Africa.

Tigerhawk looks at "Liono what are you really?" 

Liono laughs "Well the old Autobots had some info on the vok from the 
Covenant of Primus and experimented with that data before the test were 
stopped by Rodimus Prime there were 2 sparkles protoforms left" Liono Lifts 
his right shoulder plate to show a number 2  "Rodimus Prime and RC gave me 
half there sparks and use the matrix to create a whole one."

Tigerhawk looks "That's you what about the first one?"

Liono's face changes "That's not our concern right now lets move to Africa" 
starts to walk.
